---
title: Thai Beef Satay with Crispy Broccoli, Peanut Sauce, and Jasmine Rice
description: This Thai favorite shouldn’t be limited to your takeout order –it’s just as easy to make it at home. A sweet and savory marinade is the secret to juicy, flavorful skewers. We can’t get enough of this creamy peanut sauce – it’s good on just about everything.
